		    <div class="comment-content"><p>THE BEST RED VELVET CAKE EVER!!!!   =)<br />
I&#8217;m over the moon about this cake!!!  Every other RV recipe I&#8217;ve tried has been good in flavor but on the dry side.  WAY on the dry side!!  But I kept making it, hoping it would change.  LOL  It has changed now!!!!  YIPPEE!!!  Thank you Paula!!  <img src='http://www.bellalimento.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' /><br />
I have tried several of your recipes and will try many more!!  Thanks a million!!  <img src='http://www.bellalimento.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' /><br />
My boys say this Red Velvet Cake is the BOMB!!!!!  <img src='http://www.bellalimento.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
